user.description:
Monitored MACs: use a JSON array of objects with name and mac, for example:
[
  {"name": "Notebook", "mac": "aa:bb:cc:dd:ee:ff"},
  {"name": "Phone", "mac": "11:22:33:44:55:66"}
]
Legacy format still works: one MAC per line (or comma-separated).

